{"tid":2200170,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"許智峯：民主派絕跡 林鄭最開心","createTime":"2020-09-12T17:54:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-13T08:19:39.000Z","uid":51469,"like":6,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f7512a67db0bd34b0b61d33d888f465494fee650","tid":2200170,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T17:54:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200912/O37V6S62NVEOBHBFUU4AERP764/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200912%2FO37V6S62NVEOBHBFUU4AERP764%2F&d=O8bnHDCsQiwN1SoPxP513cg1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=65c00572\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200912%2FO37V6S62NVEOBHBFUU4AERP764%2F&h=047f5975\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200912/O37V6S62NVEOBHBFUU4AERP764/</a><br />\n<br />\n【去留議會●議會抗爭篇】「招呼」林鄭為民出氣VS不能因此接受「委任」安排<br />\n<br />\n林鄭上任特首初期，曾承諾為加強與立法會溝通，將每月一次到立法會出席30分鐘的「短問短答」質詢環節，同時繼續出席一年4次的特首答問大會。然而在林鄭去年拒絕答應反送中運動的五大訴求，並一直無視警暴問題下，民主派議員多次在她現身立法會時抗議。<br />\n<br />\n許智峯：缺少反對票或令結果被扭曲<br />\n<br />\n難忍民主派反對聲音，林鄭最終於去年12月「打倒昨日的我」，透過特首辦聲稱由於去年10月現身立法會公佈《施政報告》和出席答問大會時，都遇到民主派議員激烈抗議及阻撓會議，根本不能正常溝通，因此要重新檢視其「短問短答」質詢安排，之後未見再有相關環節。而民主派多次力促她現身立法會就「港版國安法」解畫，她亦一直龜縮，自今年1月後，到近日宣佈會於10月14日重返立法會宣讀《施政報告》。<br />\n<br />\n事隔9個月後重現立法會，議事廳內的民主派，屆時反而未必出現，或只剩下一片唱好大讚的建制聲音。主留派的民主黨許智峯接受《蘋果》查詢時指，由於林鄭施政乏善可陳，近年林鄭現身立法會時，均遭民主派議員大力「招呼」，包括試過在林鄭進場和離開時均高喊口號並上前抗議，及在答問大會向林鄭提出尖銳質詢，「我哋亦試過喺林鄭身後投射『五大訴求，缺一不可』字樣，將香港人嘅訴求直接喺立法會表達」，許強調：「呢啲都係好重要嘅畫面，可以幫香港人出返啖氣。」<br />\n<br />\n他並指，《施政報告》的致謝議案投票結果，傳統上被視為特首表現的「寒暑表」，若然民主派議員全數絕迹於議會，相信最高興的是見到《施政報告》在無反對票下獲得通過的林鄭，尤其林鄭竟能在推動國安惡法後，仍獲立法會通過致謝，「相信香港巿民到時見到，只會更加激氣，我亦擔心呢個結果出到嚟，會令唔知情嘅國際傳媒以為立法會呢個機構真係好感謝林鄭」。"},{"pid":"54d64b6c70cd23322c85464d04f6b8e12d644238","tid":2200170,"uid":294121,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T17:56:47.000Z","msg":"招呼完，之後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b04cace40e78b0e7ac596af1b487c630b4b27ac3","tid":2200170,"uid":259901,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T17:57:43.000Z","msg":"有咩唔好<br />\n最好立法會就同全國人大一樣，份份議案都全票通過，等全世界睇下中国香港係點同偉大祖國接軌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4786eba72329a7af288835a95e37e49b3184365","tid":2200170,"uid":140538,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T17:59:16.000Z","msg":"起底，block<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd2cab7b0bc4b3952fc9a4aef83cf28b6a2563fa","tid":2200170,"uid":39010,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T18:02:40.000Z","msg":"是但啦屌 咪撚煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0084cf567bab5c1c14ae9a7eb42b4e47c102968","tid":2200170,"uid":8014,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"54d64b6c70cd23322c85464d04f6b8e12d644238","tid":2200170,"uid":294121,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T17:56:47.000Z","msg":"招呼完，之後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T18:09:33.000Z","msg":"之後開記招話今日係民豬最黑暗時刻<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n泛民想做on9野：各有各做，兄弟爬山<br />\n<br />\n做錯左：不指責，不分化，鬧佢都無用，諗下點補救，應該要屌政府而唔係屌泛民，黃絲狙擊泛民 會中港共計 港共最開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n泛民永遠立於不敗之地"},{"pid":"dd054793f8a82705980ec122e0f9040f15dfac20","tid":2200170,"uid":51469,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b4786eba72329a7af288835a95e37e49b3184365","tid":2200170,"uid":140538,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T17:59:16.000Z","msg":"起底，block<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T18:20:24.000Z","msg":"唔想見到就BLOCK?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e75a3594e1e5ab7a6df13e53a499d13b877bd405","tid":2200170,"uid":337336,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T18:26:46.000Z","msg":"許智峯左膠"},{"pid":"7d80b85fa39a1706d939d8eb0a75da84d13e5382","tid":2200170,"uid":343798,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T18:28:39.000Z","msg":"鄭月娥最開心一定係民主黨肯繼續做呢場戲 做忠誠反對派"},{"pid":"2b6012d55aa94bacbcb5742027b21500f2938634","tid":2200170,"uid":319935,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"b4786eba72329a7af288835a95e37e49b3184365","tid":2200170,"uid":140538,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T17:59:16.000Z","msg":"起底，block<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T19:22:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />賈雨村出哂名<br />\n我欣賞佢咁耐都冇改名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d9b5b630cbce3ea2a5962605dd93f02c14e90c2","tid":2200170,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"2b6012d55aa94bacbcb5742027b21500f2938634","tid":2200170,"uid":319935,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"b4786eba72329a7af288835a95e37e49b3184365","tid":2200170,"uid":140538,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"202